# 📸 Photo Filter Web App

A simple and interactive photo filter web application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Upload images from your device
- Apply filters like grayscale
- Instant preview on canvas
- Lightweight and fast

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Canvas API)

